Installation instructions are documented in the manual 
available in manual/trimaran-4.0-manual.pdf 

The latest version of the manual is always available at
http://www.trimaran.org/

The manual also includes instructions for using the compiler
and simulator, and guides on how carry out compiler and 
architecture research using Trimaran. 

Please report any bugs you encounter in the documentation,
or difficulties with the installation process, to the Trimaran
support team at support@trimaran.org.

Active users and developers may wish to join the mailing list.
For more information, or to join, visit
http://www.trimaran.org/support.shtml
